      • findMethod

        public static Method findMethod(String methodName,
                                ReflectMember.Match match,
                                ReflectClass rclass,
                                ReflectParameterTypes parameterTypes)
                         throws ReflectMember.ReflectMemberException
        Search in a ReflectClass for a method. This method might also search super and parent classes, depending on the Match value parsed.
        Parameters:
        methodName - The name of the method
        match - How deep the method should search
        rclass - The class to search in
        parameterTypes - Parameter types of the method that should be found
        Throws:
        ReflectMemberException - Thrown if the method could not be found
        ReflectMember.ReflectMemberException
